#

Saffron Risotto with Grilled Asparagus and Parmesan

40 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseVegetarian Dish

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodVegetarian

Description

A creamy, luxurious risotto infused with saffron, paired with tender grilled asparagus and a sprinkle of parmesan for a delightful meal.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • saffron threads: 1/4 teaspoon
  • grated parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • asparagus: 1 bunch
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • onion, finely chopped: 1
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
